snippet: Three teams from Webster University of St. Louis were among the top six finishers at the Pan-American Intercollegiate Championships in Lubbock, Tex.
abstract: Dylan Loeb McClain Chess column notes that all three teams from Webster University in St Louis are among top six finishers in Pan-American Intercollegiate Team Chess Championship, continuing team's domination of college chess.
lead_paragraph: Three teams from Webster University of St. Louis were among the top six finishers at the Pan-American Intercollegiate Championships in Lubbock, Tex.

headline.print_headline: Webster Strengthens Grip On the Collegiate Game
headline.main: Webster Strengthens Grip on the Collegiate Game
